item.title: Warmup Snissnap
item.description:
Description

We were given a file snissnap_besked.txt containing a sequence of hexadecimal values. The challenge description hinted at a “Warmup” task.

Recon

The file content looked like this: MWEgMDQgNGQgMDQgNDAgMDQgMzUgMDQgMjAgMDAgMmUgMDQg...
